  .row
    .col-sm-4
      h3.text-center 
        i.icon.ion-funnel
        |  Moderating Questions
      p.lead The most important questions are often not heard or answered. QuestionCookie lets the crowd source and vote on the best questions.
    .col-sm-4
      h3.text-center 
        i.icon.ion-cash
        |  Free and Easy to Use
      p.lead Don't pay for another question moderation service. 1) Enter a unique event name above to start your question cookie. 2) Then share the URL with participants.
